# The consensus and genesis-generator builds use this directory as their
# context. Send only the Dockerfiles and the two source inputs actually copied
# by Dockerfile.genesis-generator; local dumps and generated endpoint data may
# contain development credentials.
*
!Dockerfile.genesis-generator
!Dockerfile.qrysm-consensus
!vm64_genesis_gqrl.py
!qrysm-deposit-runtime/
qrysm-deposit-runtime/*
!qrysm-deposit-runtime/main.go
